nnoremap <S-k> <Plug>MoveLineUp
nnoremap <S-h> <Plug>MoveCharLeft
nnoremap <S-l> <Plug>MoveCharRight
vnoremap <S-j> <Plug>MoveBlockDown
vnoremap <S-k> <Plug>MoveBlockUp
